{"tid":2356353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「對唔住」係最簡單嘅三個字，但亦都係最難講嘅一句話。","createTime":"2021-01-06T18:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:08:04.000Z","uid":199081,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b213f84df91f65c669c1a28dc2c1b0f44b8198","tid":2356353,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T18:19:40.000Z","msg":"警世+趁佢未撚死最後尾刀<br />\n柒咗咪柒咗囉<br />\n認柒道歉有幾難呀<br />\n道咗歉咪間唔中笑你一兩句<br />\n但放唔低自尊企硬死唔認錯<br />\n仲要諉過於人老屈人波台狗<br />\n搞到喺波台魚台動物台財經台硬件台軟件台創意台上班台積怨落嚟嘅人一齊討伐圍插<br />\n柒到俾人爆對話紀錄爆名爆身型<br />\n玩到要自爆保平安<br />\n一切嘅事講緊早廿個鐘講句「對唔住我唔應該笑唔健全嘅手足，唔應該老屈人藍屍，唔應該煽動其他人入原po恥笑」就可以完<br />\n上連登已經唔show名唔show樣冇人知你乜水（唔計感情台搵食約咗人出嚟嘅話）<br />\n你都放唔低唔知喺邊度嚟嘅自尊<br />\n咁就抵你死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇於承擔做錯咗嘅事再道歉真係好重要"},{"pid":"6808180450eb2dc8e72f5831e00380b9116fb79d","tid":2356353,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"9add5371b68818e8304982861c2c037b37f24ba0","tid":2356353,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6808180450eb2dc8e72f5831e00380b9116fb79d","tid":2356353,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"ok"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"挽留眼帶嗎"},{"pid":"f6fa94c944714fc3b2f2c023937d44429ae195ac","tid":2356353,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9add5371b68818e8304982861c2c037b37f24ba0","tid":2356353,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6808180450eb2dc8e72f5831e00380b9116fb79d","tid":2356353,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"ok"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"挽留眼帶嗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T18:25:29.000Z","msg":"乜水"},{"pid":"485332